init_text: Your entire life, you've been told you're deathly allergic to bees. You've always had people protecting you from them, be it your mother or a hired hand. Today, one slips through and lands on your shoulder. You hear a tiny voice say "Your Majesty, what are your orders?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You look from the bee to all your wealth.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Your eyes return to the bee.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Build me the largest honey farm on Earth," you say.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I never want to see it again."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You wave your hand and the bee flies away.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The bees follow their orders, tearing down the palace and building a honey farm.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The honey farm produces more honey than ever before, and soon the bees are ordered to build a second huge honey farm, then a third.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The bees do exactly what you tell them to.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But, one day, the bees come back and say "Your Majesty, we have built the honey farms you ordered.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: We have enough honey to last the rest of your life, and beyond.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "That's very brave of you," you say.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You take a bite of honey and laugh.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "You see, I've decided to build a new palace."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Besides, you've already ordered us to build the largest palace in the world."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "The largest palace in the world," you say, "isn't enough.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I want the largest palace in the Multiverse.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: And you're going to build it for me.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The bees look at each other, then back up at you.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Your body tenses up and your face turns red.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Your eyes go wide and your tongue turns black.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You fall to the ground, gripping your throat.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "You pushed us too far," the same bee says.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: As you lay dying, the bees' laughter slowly fades and the sound of a river rushing by fills your ears.
